TextEng: "You put your hand in the grinder on purpose?"
"Lazy, would you know the Reaper's True Name?"
"The grinder had better be fixed soon or Gru'ul will be angry."
Text: "분쇄기를 빨리 고쳐야 할 텐데, 아니면 그루울이 화낼 거야."

TextEng: "I talked to Gru'ul. He's given you a holiday."
<StartCheck>[Dexterity]</Start> <StartAction>Dismantle the grinder and free the imp.</Start>
"How did your hand get stuck in the grinder, anyway?"
Text: "어쨌든, 손이 어떻게 분쇄기에 끼게 된 거야?"

TextEng: "You put your hand in the grinder on purpose?"
"Lazy, would you know the Reaper's True Name?"
"Calm down. Everything's going to be all right."
"Your arm's mangled. You can't work like that."
Text: "네 팔이 엉망이야. 그 상태로는 일 못 해."
